幼蟲的[[寄主|寄主]]植物包括<ref name=f2018>Condamine, F. L. (2018). Limited by the roof of the world: mountain radiations of Apollo swallowtails controlled by diversity-dependence processes. Biology letters, 14(3), 20170622.</ref><ref>Allio, R., Nabholz, B., Wanke, S., Chomicki, G., Pérez-Escobar, O. A., Cotton, A. M., ... & Condamine, F. L. (2020). Genome-wide macroevolutionary signatures of key innovations in butterflies colonizing new host plants. bioRxiv.</ref>：
* [[馬兜鈴科|馬兜鈴科]]（[[虎鳳蝶族|虎鳳蝶族]]和[[鋸鳳蝶族|鋸鳳蝶族]]）
